# 🍽️ Food Waste Donation Platform

A web platform designed to reduce food waste by connecting **restaurants, hostels, and households** with nearby **NGOs** who can collect leftover food.

---

## 🚀 Features

✅ Donors can register and upload details of leftover food  
✅ NGOs can view available donations in their area  
✅ Real-time data from MongoDB  
✅ Clean and responsive UI using React.js  
✅ Secure backend with Node.js and Express  

---

## 🧠 Technologies Used

| Category | Technology |
|-----------|-------------|
| Frontend | React.js, HTML, CSS, JavaScript |
| Backend | Node.js, Express.js |
| Database | MongoDB |
| Design | Figma |

